metadata.name: The SUN, inner strength
metadata.description:
My first NFT ever !!!

Size: 4724 x 4730 Pixels or 40 x40 cm 300dpi scan

The sun gives us the conditions for life, gives us energy and brings light.

Images of the sun came to me in a beautiful vision of light. People describe them as pure energy.

Throughout history, the sun has been worshiped in various cultures. Even today, he is revered by most religions, including Christianity. 

Apollo is one of the Olympian deities Greek and Roman mythology. Apollo has been recognized as a god of archery, music and dance, truth and prophecy, healing and diseases, the Sun and light, poetry, and more. 

My name Apolonia comes from the Greek Apollo.
